                     <interp inst="t17980912-45-punish261" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980912-45-defend468 t17980912-45-punish261"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Jacobs, <rs id="t17980912-45-verdict262" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980912-45-verdict262" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs> (Aged 53.)</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17980912-45-punish263" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980912-45-punish263" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980912-45-defend470 t17980912-45-punish263"></join>
               Transported for fourteen years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. COMMON SERJEANT.</p>
